# 9x8 character sitting on the couch. Same face layout (8 wide, eyes
# separated by 2 skin pixels) as standing/seated so eyes don't merge at
# half-block scale. Legs split so it reads as "seated" from top-down.
@frame 0
. n H H H H n .
n H H H H H H n
H S e S S e S H
. S S S m S S .
. n S S S S n .
B B B B B B B B
B B B B B B B B
. B B . . B B .
. S S . . S S .
